    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a rut though. it's like the more i try to fix it, the more i realize that the only constant is the failure. it's exhausting to keep waking up and starting the same cycle of struggle. sometimes it feels like there's no way out of the loop except to just... stop.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
